Nbd2 {This type of passive play leads nowhere for White.} Re8 {[%cal 
Ge8e4,Gf5e4,Gd5e4,Bc7c6,Bd8f6][%csl Ge4] Black now has the more active position, 
keeping the strong knight on e4.} *

