is punished swiftly.} Bxe5 13. dxe5 Qb6+ {[%cal Gb6g1][%csl Rg1]} 14. Kh1 Nf2+ 
{[%cal Bf5d3,Gb6f2][%csl Rd3] With a huge advantage for Black.} *

